  "text": "The single-threaded version of ROOT-Sim also offers innovative transparent supports for LP migration and load balancing [CITATION_1] , which will be considered as a reference for the assessment of the currently presented load-sharing version in terms of the ability to exploit the computing resources offered by a multi-core machine when the actual simulation workload dynamically varies over time.",
